JOINT_MAX = 87: Represents the size of the Joint enum.

flags JointFlags:
JOINT_FLAG_ORIENTATION_VALID = 1: The joint's orientation data is valid.
JOINT_FLAG_ORIENTATION_TRACKED = 2: The joint's orientation is actively tracked. May not be set if tracking has been temporarily lost.
JOINT_FLAG_POSITION_VALID = 4: The joint's position data is valid.
JOINT_FLAG_POSITION_TRACKED = 8: The joint's position is actively tracked. May not be set if tracking has been temporarily lost.
