Document: XRBodyTracker
Path: godot/classes/class_xrbodytracker.rst
Summary: This section describes methods for getting and setting joint flags and transforms for an XR body tracker.

Method: get_joint_flags(joint: Joint) → bitfield[JointFlags]
Returns flags about the validity of the tracking data for the given body joint.

Method: get_joint_transform(joint: Joint) → Transform3D
Returns the transform for the given body joint.

Method: set_joint_flags(joint: Joint, flags: bitfield[JointFlags]) → void
Sets flags about the validity of the tracking data for the given body joint.

Method: set_joint_transform(joint: Joint, transform: Transform3D) → void
Sets the transform for the given body joint.